      "para_id": "Q001084.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) When En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , chosen by Nanše in the heart , the child born to Lugal-Uruba , the child of Aya-kurgal , ruler of Lagaš , built the Ebgal for Inana , made the E-ana exceed all the mountains , and decorated it with gold and silver , then his servant , Id-lusikil , his personal quarters’ scribe , fashioned ( this ) inscribed clay nail for himself ."
    }
  ],
